org.apache.hama.bsp.sync

Interface PeerSyncClient

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SyncClient
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BSPPeerSyncClient, LocalBSPRunner.LocalSyncClient, ZooKeeperSyncClientImpl

    public interface PeerSyncClient
extends SyncClient
    PeerSyncClient defines the behavior that a BSPPeer performs to maintain synchronized global state as it progresses.

      • getAllPeerNames

        String[] getAllPeerNames(BSPJobID jobID)
        Returns all registered tasks within the sync daemon. They have to be ordered ascending by their task id.
        Parameters:
        jobID - the job ID
        Returns:
        an ordered string array of host:port pairs of all tasks connected to the daemon.
